{"id": "1407352329497214996", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "・強化演習で全キャラを１回ずつクリアする。これでヘブンズコアが２０個もらえる。\n　ガチャ４回分と考えるとバカにできないので早めに！\n・レベルはある程度まんべんなく。\n・最初は深海ガチャでキャラを揃えるのをおすすめ。", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:15:42.694000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "yatta", "emoji_id": "1390953053322219530", "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467", "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1407354435713241159", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1039303411025322034", "author_name": "supicq7", "author_bot": false, "content": "深海パーティが一番強くて使いやすいって感じですかね？", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:24:04.855000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1407354735886864445", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "キャラにブレが少ないです。触手君は毎ターン1本増えて、プレイヤーフェイズとエネミーフェイズの間に自動で前から攻撃してくれます。", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:25:16.422000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1407354948022173747", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "これが最初だと本当に強くて、手段の少ない最初の方はかなり助かります。", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:26:06.999000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1407355843829039104", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1039303411025322034", "author_name": "supicq7", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほどです〜\n事前情報なしで始めたら自然と赤パーティになってしまったのでそのうち使ってみたいです", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:29:40.576000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1407356396726653030", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "狂魔は自傷しちゃうので、最初に使うとちょっとやりにくいかもですね。。。", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:31:52.397000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1407356818945998979", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1039303411025322034", "author_name": "supicq7", "author_bot": false, "content": "HP50%以上残しでクリアの報酬取れなくて悲しいです…", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:33:33.062000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:33:50.207000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1407357110886469702", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "ぶっちゃけある程度章が進んでからお礼参りすれば大丈夫です", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:34:42.666000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1407357245053993110", "channel_id": "1407352329497214996", "type": 0, "author_id": "1039303411025322034", "author_name": "supicq7", "author_bot": false, "content": "とりあえずストーリーやりまくります！", "timestamp": "2025-08-19T13:35:14.654000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407352329497214996", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "早めにやっておいた方がいいこと", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
